  "title": "Insurance Product Owner",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a insurance product owner whowill be required to identify and analyze\nbusiness pain points, gaps, core problems, industry trends and business needs\nand translate these to tangible business requirements and needs.<br /></p><p>Job Scope:<br /></p><ul><li>Be the point person to work with the Partner business analyst team in managing the requirements and prioritization for product / feature launches</li><li>Manage technology partners</li><li>Drive requirement workshops to finalize requirements</li><li>Work with the design teams in defining customer journeys across standalone and embedded propositions. </li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree or equivalent qualification</li><li>Minimum 6 years+ experience as a BA</li><li>Experience in Digital Delivery in Agile environment</li><li>Prior experience on e-commerce, customer lifecycle, digital sales, customer servicing, insurance products</li><li>Formal Business Analysis qualification and Agile qualification/certifications </li><li>Prior experience on Product/platform lifecycle management</li></ul><p>If you are keen on the above position, reach out to Christopher Shepherdson (EA Licence No: 11C5502 | EAP Registration No: R1877011) at cshepherdson@morganmckinley.com or contact +65 6818 3193 for a confidential chat.</p>",
